gomodel:SYNGO_4184  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: - Postembedding immunogold EM of adult rat cerebral cortex was performed using 254.2 anti-liprin2-antibody.\n\n- Fig. 5C EM images show the expression of gold particles associated with the presynaptic membrane.. Experimental description: Rat hippocampal neuron cultures were prepared from hippocampi dissected from E18 rat embryos as described (Goslin and Banker, 1991)." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7620-2704" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1558-1958" ;
